<small>{{font|color=#0000FF|81}}</small>{{font|color=#000000| Neither shalt thou stand against the blood of thy neighbour; I am the LORD.}}

<small>{{font|color=#0000FF|82}}</small>{{font|color=#000000| Thou shalt not hate thy brother in thine heart: thou shalt in any wise rebuke thy neighbour, and not suffer sin upon him.}}

